	   0  LOAD&PUSH (0)
	   2  LOADCON&PUSH [1]	    ;  (2)
	   4  CALL 2 [2]	    ;  <
	   7  JUMPNIL 8
	  10  LOADCON [0]	    ;  1
	  12  NOOP
	  13  JUMP 19
	  16  LOAD&PUSH (0)
	  18  LOAD&PUSH (0)
